##
## Umbraco CMS
##

# JSON schema files for appsettings.json
appsettings-schema.json
appsettings-schema.*.json

# JSON schema for umbraco-package.json
umbraco-package-schema.json

# Packages created from the backoffice
**/umbraco/Data/CreatedPackages/

# Temp folder (Examine indexes, NuCache, MediaCache, etc.)
**/umbraco/Data/TEMP/

# SQLite database files
**/umbraco/Data/*.sqlite.db
**/umbraco/Data/*.sqlite.db-shm
**/umbraco/Data/*.sqlite.db-wal

